      public void commitInvoice(String invoiceId) throws ApiException
      Commit Invoice This endpoint is used to commit an invoice for a given invoice id. Once committed, the invoice is considered to be finalized.
      Parameters:
      invoiceId - The unique identifier of the invoice at the Tax Service Adapter or Tax Service Provider. (required)
